Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy applies to all games, apps, webs and related services of WOOMBIT PTE. LTD.("WOOMBIT", "we", "us", "our apps", "apps", "games", "apps" or "our apps"), We have created this policy to describe what information is collected, used and disclosed that belongs to you in connection with the apps.
Your privacy and data security are extremely important to us. We are committed to the responsible management, protection and use of your personal information. If you choose to use our applications or games, then you consent to the collection and use of information in connection with this policy. The personal information we collect will be used to provide and improve our services. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
1. WHAT INFORMATION WE COLLECT
We collect the following information:
(a).
Data about your device, such as system language; device memory; screen resolution; device model.
(b).
Your IP address; MCC; country code;  Google Ad ID, which you can reset or remove at any time in your device settings.
(c).
Data about the version code; version name; package name; operating system; operating system version.
(d).
Data about your actions in the application, for example, opening a page.
2. HOW WE USE COLLECTED DATA AND WHY
We may use the information for the following purpose:
(a).
To analyzing users interact with our apps or games to improve the services and provide better user experience.
(b).
The Feedback you provide helps us respond to your users service requests more efficiently.
(c).
For third party analytics and third party advertising services - Express consent.
(d).
To fix the crash and ANR issues on some special devices.
