4. USER RIGHTS
You may submit a request to us to delete your personal data if you found the below situation, sending us at email: dev@woombit.com.
(a).
Your personal data is no longer necessary for data collection or processing.
(b).
You have withdrawn your consent to our processing of your personal data.
(c).
Your personal data has been processed illegally.
5. OUR POLICES ABOUT CHILDREN
We never willingly or knowingly collect any data related to children that under 16 years of age.
6. DATA SECURITY AND RESERVATION
We take reasonable measures to help us with protecting the data we collect. And we retain the data we collected for up to 36 months.
7. CHANGES TO THE PRIVACY POLICY
We reserve the right to change, modify or otherwise alter this Policy at any time in our sole discretion. You can always review the latest version of our app privacy policy. Please review this Privacy Policy regularly to ensure that you are kept informed of any changes. You may stop using our apps immediately only if you do not agree to any changes to this policy. Your continued use of any game after the publication of any changes to this Policy constitutes your acceptance of the revised Policy. Please note that our employees or agents have no right to change any of our policies.
8. POLITICAL OR RELIGIOUS BELIEFS
Bible Daily will not collect your religious beliefs. By default, the users of our app are Christians.
9. CONTACT US
If you have any questions or suggestions about the Privacy Policy, you may contact us at email: dev@woombit.com.